{"tid":1021992,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"投胎入場券","createTime":"2019-02-14T15:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T16:19:28.000Z","uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a568151250eeea0ba256e4300db304e4b03f1bc2","tid":1021992,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:44:59.000Z","msg":"而家香港真係無撚曬希望，美支貿易戰都唔知最後傾成點，隨時都會失業，闔球剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n所以我而家間唔中都會加下班，加夠兩個鐘就有120蚊，夠我每個月買一次重新投胎入場券。雖然機會率只係有1400萬分之一，都好過完全無希望，走去跳樓，大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw，其實人窮真係唔應該生仔，劣質基因仲學人生仔真係應該捉去人道毀滅，所以元首的優生學就係想重整世界秩序，點知比班邪惡國家破壞咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHeil Hitler! Heil Mein F&uuml;hrer!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rrX9Ev9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrrX9Ev9.png&h=f1726567&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d9589ebcec9e6a71a4569601c72bf255f423a80","tid":1021992,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T15:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVChOsk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVChOsk.jpg&h=4102aeab&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"22c02a76ec5b4e868b167527266d86d4001692a8","tid":1021992,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:19:28.000Z","msg":"55"}]}